3 classes
CLI class- controller- what communicates with my user
Cocktail class- where objects are created to display
API class- bring in external data, consume api here, instatiate object

"https://www.thecocktaildb.com/api/json/v1/1/filter.php?i=#{ingredient}"  #cocktails by ingredient name
"https://www.thecocktaildb.com/api/json/v1/1/lookup.php?i=#{idnumber}"     #cocktail by idnumber